sentences: Kazuki Kato (加藤 和樹, Katō Kazuki, October 7, 1984) is a Japanese actor, voice actor and singer from Nagoya, Aichi Prefecture.
In 2011, he formed a band called Joker and their first single debuted on December 7, 2011.
